These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk
City: new-york, marseilles
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Beverage   | 7up  | almond-milk |
| City     | marseilles | new-york  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, may
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Beverage    | almond-milk      | soy-milk         |
| Birthday   | november | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, azure
House: gothic-revival, craftsman
1. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Color   | azure | mauve   |
| House       | craftsman  | gothic-revival |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, project-manager
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, trike
1. the project-manager is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Job   | fisherman  | project-manager |
| Transport         | van | trike    |

 #################################

 
